01:31.980 --> 01:33.600
And perfect, as you can see,

01:33.600 --> 01:36.870
we are logged in into our Windows 11 computer

01:36.870 --> 01:40.740
which is running as a virtual machine inside VMware player

01:40.740 --> 01:43.560
inside my Apple silicon computer.

01:43.560 --> 01:45.720
So if I go ahead here on the right

01:45.720 --> 01:48.240
and click on the virtual machine library,

01:48.240 --> 01:51.030
as you can see I have Kali installed in here,

01:51.030 --> 01:53.760
and now I have Windows which I can run

01:53.760 --> 01:55.770
by simply clicking on start,

01:55.770 --> 01:58.653
but right now it's already running, so I can't stop it.

01:59.730 --> 02:02.820
