02:02.820 --> 02:05.790
and here it's saying it is not connected to the internet,

02:05.790 --> 02:09.750
because we need to install the VMware tools on it

02:09.750 --> 02:13.050
which will install the drivers for the virtual interfaces

02:13.050 --> 02:15.120
so that we can access virtual networks,

02:15.120 --> 02:17.640
and it'll also install the display drivers

02:17.640 --> 02:20.280
and enable a lot of usability features.

02:20.280 --> 02:23.310
To do that, we're gonna go to the virtual machine here,

02:23.310 --> 02:26.820
and we're gonna click Reinstall VMware Tools.

02:26.820 --> 02:28.203
We're gonna click Install,

02:29.310 --> 02:33.330
and this will basically mount a DVD drive on this computer.

02:33.330 --> 02:36.270
And as you can see, we have a notification in here

02:36.270 --> 02:39.510
telling us that a new DVD drive is detected,

02:39.510 --> 02:42.420
