03:04.740 --> 03:08.853
in order to install VMware tools on this virtual machine.

03:10.230 --> 03:12.690
Once the PowerShell blue screen disappears,

03:12.690 --> 03:15.120
it means that everything got installed properly.

03:15.120 --> 03:16.500
And if you look here at the bottom,

03:16.500 --> 03:20.220
you'll see that we have network connection through ethernet,

03:20.220 --> 03:22.440
and that's because this machine is configured

03:22.440 --> 03:25.860
to use the virtual net network that VMware starts.

03:25.860 --> 03:28.080
And I have my virtual machines configured

03:28.080 --> 03:29.520
to get internet access.

03:29.520 --> 03:32.220
And like we said before, this way these machines

03:32.220 --> 03:34.440
