03:38.130 --> 03:40.410
and get internet access through it.

03:40.410 --> 03:43.743
And to confirm this, we can simply open up a web browser,

03:45.810 --> 03:48.633
get started, and just go to google.com.

03:50.490 --> 03:53.850
And perfect, as you can see, now we have internet access

03:53.850 --> 03:55.263
on this virtual machine.

